com.schlimm.springcdi.decorator.resolver.rules
Interface IgnoreDecoratorAutowiringLogic

public interface IgnoreDecoratorAutowiringLogic

Tagging interface to mark a DependencyDescriptor that was instantiated during decorator autowiring logic. The DecoratorAwareAutowireCandidateResolver will ignore specific DecoratorAutowiringRules for DependencyDescriptor that is marked with this interface.

Author:
Niklas Schlimm
See Also:
DecoratorAwareAutowireCandidateResolver, SimpleDelegateResolutionStrategy
